Prerequisite
Domain Controller (DC)
Domain Name Server (DNS)
3 features of windows ADK (Deployment Tools, User State Migration Tool and Window PE) need to be installed to use MDT
MDT can be installed in any computer

Installation Link

ADK - https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-hardware/get-started/adk-install (2 downloads, Windows ADK and Windows PE add-on for the ADK)
MDT - https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=54259


